title: Business Formations within 8 Quarters for District of Columbia (DISCONTINUED)
notes:
The Business Formation Statistics are now released on a monthly basis, and the quarterly series will no longer be updated. See BFBF8QTOTALSADC (https://fred.stlouisfed.org/series/BFBF8QTOTALSADC) for an alternative.

The number of employer businesses that originate from Business Applications (BA) within eight quarters from the quarter of application, similar to https://fred.stlouisfed.org/series/BF4QSADC. By definition, the end-point of this series is determined by the most recent quarter for which the administrative data is available on payroll.
